        <Parent_String>side-blown trumpets [300042361], trumpets (aerophones) [300042339], lip-vibrated aerophones with cylindrical bore [300209194], lip-vibrated aerophones [300041639], aerophones [300041622], sound devices by acoustical characteristics [300041621], sound devices (equipment) [300387677], Sound Devices (hierarchy name) [300041619], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
